We go from talking too much to not talking at all. We can sit there and not say a single word. That is why people think we are slow most of the time. We are not slow. We just don’t feel comfortable talking in that particular company.

name: ELIOTT
description: #Designer of books aka #Formatting Services | Author of novels | Spewer of profanities | Gen X | Caustic | #JOMO | #Aspie | Ace | They/Them/Heathen 🖤🤍💜

Don’t push us away. Listen to us. Or just tell us to stop. It’s not that hard. We won’t mind. We will, however, mind if you laugh at us. Because we try so hard to fit in, it hurts like hell when we realize we failed once again. And someone laughing at us makes it even worse.

Don't do it. It's as simple as that.
